thread.title: Mobile World: creative device developers eye 5G tech

title: Mobile World: creative device developers eye 5G tech
text:
Mobile World: creative device developers eye 5G tech Wednesday, February 28, 2018 - 01:43 
Creative devices developed by 5G technologies have been a key theme at the 2018 Mobile World Congress. As Ivor Bennett reports, big network suppliers made the case that next generation wireless may arrive sooner than previously forecast.
